===Etymology===
From the Greek [[ἀναχωρέω]] anachōreō, signifying "to withdraw", "to depart into the country outside the circumvallated city"

===Noun===
'''anchorite'''
#One who lives in isolation or seclusion, especially for relgious reasons.  

